              "prompt": "Create a React + TypeScript login form component in src/components/LoginForm.tsx for the dashboard app. Include: email and password fields with controlled state, client-side validation (email format, min 8 char password), loading state during async submit, error display, proper TypeScript types, and accessibility attributes. Follow existing project conventions from the components directory.",
